                        <interp inst="t18360815-1842-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 22.—
<rs id="t18360815-1842-punishment-71" type="punishmentDescription">
