                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1842-18360815 t18360815-1842-punishment-71"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Baron Gurney</hi>.</p>
